# Real-Time Collaborative Note App

A real-time collaborative note-taking application built with **React**, **Node.js**, **Express**, **MongoDB**, and **Socket.io**. Users can create, edit, and collaborate on notes in real time.

---

## Features

- Real-time note creation and updates using **Socket.io**
- Collaborative editing with multiple users in a room
- Track **active collaborators** for each note
- Display **last updated time** for each note
- Notifications when a user joins or leaves a room
- CRUD operations for notes
- Responsive and user-friendly UI using **React** and **Tailwind CSS**
- Role-based actions: Admin and regular collaborators

---

## Technologies Used

- **Frontend:** React, Redux, React Router, Tailwind CSS  
- **Backend:** Node.js, Express.js  
- **Database:** MongoDB (Mongoose ODM)  
- **Real-Time Communication:** Socket.io  
- **Version Control:** Git, GitHub

